{"tid":2505684,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"另一半太蠢點搞呀","createTime":"2021-04-26T21:13:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T21:45:05.000Z","uid":59501,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"42db86ed5bc9c1fd36126096cdc3c0aabcb3ef1e","tid":2505684,"uid":59501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T21:13:12.000Z","msg":"一開始都唔覺佢係咁<br />\n依家發現佢好基本既常識都好似唔識咁<br />\n中文英文數學冇樣掂<br />\n<br />\n1d簡單既單字唔識讀唔讀解<br />\n100以內既加減乘除又唔識<br />\n左右都要諗幾秒先分到<br />\n更加唔好叫佢睇地圖果d<br />\n<br />\n平時驚傷到佢自尊心已經盡量搵野讚佢鼓勵佢<br />\n忍住口唔會當面話佢蠢<br />\n等佢可以自信d會用下個腦改善下啦<br />\n不過教極都好冇乜效果咁<br />\n<br />\n但係佢又傻唔哂架喎<br />\n成日計埋d c9數貪小便宜<br />\n吃喝玩樂果陣就好撚醒<br />\n都唔知佢真傻定假蠢<br />\n<br />\n呢排仲要間唔中就問我幾時結婚<br />\n真係好撚擔心第時結婚生仔之後會點<br />\n搞唔撚掂呀大佬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e1c63a676ef0af62cd7dd1c9a71f66be44584c6","tid":2505684,"uid":160336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T21:21:14.000Z","msg":"啲女人好撚蠱惑㗎"},{"pid":"8714da65e8e50993701575161dcc8fa27baabcc4","tid":2505684,"uid":397905,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T21:22:38.000Z","msg":"同佢結婚但係唔好生仔 確保佢不能夠繁殖"},{"pid":"603339e5ee77579417c3152cc653f2d183a3dfd3","tid":2505684,"uid":59501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e1c63a676ef0af62cd7dd1c9a71f66be44584c6","tid":2505684,"uid":160336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T21:21:14.000Z","msg":"啲女人好撚蠱惑㗎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T21:22:53.000Z","msg":"成日係廁所傾點殺d男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02de5dd50039d2d6237f6a66ba050f724d17775c","tid":2505684,"uid":3177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0e1c63a676ef0af62cd7dd1c9a71f66be44584c6","tid":2505684,"uid":160336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T21:21:14.000Z","msg":"啲女人好撚蠱惑㗎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-